--------------------------
Relay
--------------------------
S -> D4
(+) -> VIN/5V
(-) -> GND
--------------------------
Battery Pump Relay
--------------------------
Battery Red (+) -> Relay COM (MIDDLE TERMNIAL)
Pump Red (+) -> Relay NO (Normally Open Terminal)
Battery Black (-) -> Connects both to ESP32 GND and Pump Black 
--------------------------
Note: All GND has to be connected all together 
--------------------------

